OL,3,CFurther bin strikes announced
OL,4,Cfollowing ongoing dispute with council
OL,6,FBin crews have voted to take up
OL,7,Ffurther strike action across South
OL,8,FTyneside.
OL,10,FThe latest walk out is expected to
OL,11,Ftake place from 1-14 May inclusive.
OL,13,FStrikes began last year after bin
OL,14,Fworkers raised a grievance with the
OL,15,Fcouncil in June over claims of
OL,16,Fbullying and mismanagement.
OL,18,FAn independent investigation into the
OL,19,Fgrievance is now said to have
OL,20,Fconcluded, with findings presented to
OL,21,Fall parties and not challenged.
