OL,3,CFurther bin strikes announced
OL,4,Cfollowing ongoing dispute with council
OL,6,FSome bin workers are said to be taking
OL,7,Faction on non-strike days, meaning
OL,8,Fsome bins are not being collected on
OL,9,Fresidents' scheduled collection days.
OL,11,FTo mitigate this, the council is
OL,12,Frolling out a programme of collections
OL,13,Facross the borough.
OL,15,FSkips have also been reinstated across
OL,16,Fthe area, which will be available
OL,17,Feveryday.
