OL,3,CFurther bin strikes announced
OL,4,Cfollowing ongoing dispute with council
OL,6,FThe GMB union said it was "legally
OL,7,Fobliged" to reballot members as it was
OL,8,Funable to resolve the ongoing dispute
OL,9,Fover the last six months.
OL,11,FIt told ITV Tyne Tees that 96% voted
OL,12,Fin favour of further strike action,
OL,13,Fand it notified the Council almost 2
OL,14,Fweeks ago.
