OL,3,CFurther bin strikes announced
OL,4,Cfollowing ongoing dispute with council
OL,6,F"We are disappointed to have to take
OL,7,Ffurther action and will always explore
OL,8,Favenues of resolution to bring this
OL,9,Fdispute to an end, but our members
OL,10,Fhave to be certain that they will not
OL,11,Fbe subject to any more bullying at
OL,12,Fwork, and we will continue to
OL,13,Fnegotiate with management until we can
OL,14,Fget to that position," the union said.
OL,16,FJonathan Tew, Chief Executive of South
OL,17,FTyneside Council said: "I know that
OL,18,Fthis will be another blow for the
OL,19,Fpeople of South Tyneside.
