OL,3,CFurther bin strikes announced
OL,4,Cfollowing ongoing dispute with council
OL,6,F"We've met 30 times with crew members
OL,7,Fand trade union officials in the last
OL,8,Ffour months alone and maintained
OL,9,Fregular communication throughout,
OL,10,Ffeedback from the crew has been
OL,11,Fpositive. The agreed action plan
OL,12,Faddresses concerns and gives all
OL,13,Fparties a constructive way forward.
OL,15,F"I'm sorry that our residents and
OL,16,Fbusinesses have had to endure this
OL,17,Fongoing action despite all efforts
OL,18,Fbeing made by the Council to bring it
OL,19,Fto an end."
